Developer Terms of Use
des:
In Dog House you bark to attract dogs, and then can choose which breeds of dog you want to adopt. Return to your Dog House to earn treats, and feed them to your dogs to teach them new barks. 

Users in the United States can get Dog House Gold, which expands how many dogs you can keep. Gold members also can adopt more dog breeds, such Corgis, Bulldogs, and Retrievers.

For those that just want to hear bark sounds, say "Barks only" to pause adopting dogs. Any dogs you already adopted will be saved for later, and can be visited again. Just keep playing and you will be asked to start collecting again.
